Rating: 3
Tasty and simple. Better than many other mustard based glazes which can overwhelm fish. Instead of broiling it, however, I roasted the salmon filet in a 450 degree oven for 10 minutes and then applied glaze and put it back in for another 5-6 minutes. That way the honey doesn't have a chance to burn. The brown rice accompaniment works perfectly.